snippet.title: OverKart 4 DLC Pak! Official Release & Real N64 Capture
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD - https://www.mediafire.com/file/rttkfvfolz5nlyk/OverKart4+DLC+Pak.zip/file

This will be applied directly to your original Mario Kart 64 copy. This will update the game to OverKart 4 AND install the DLC maps. Do NOT apply this patch to a previous copy of OverKart. Read the INSTRUCTION BOOKLET for more information on installation and details on all the new game functions!

Real N64 Video Capture of the new OverKart 4 DLC Pak, available for download free! The OverKart 4 DLC Pak is a new addition to the OverKart 4 mod that adds 8 BRAND NEW levels to the game, available in Custom Set 2. This expands the total number of custom levels to 24! I'm very excited to bring this new work to you, and hope that you enjoy it!
